      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing a level of mechanical preservation rarely seen. The S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six remains the centerpiece, featuring a recently overhauled VANOS system and treated rod bearings for ultimate peace of mind. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via a factory M Variable Differential Lock. This chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high-load cornering. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping, and the throttle response from the individual throttle bodies is immediate and linear. Every bushing, seal, and fluid is up to date, making this a turn-key example for the discerning collector who demands peak atmospheric performance.",
